sentences.en: Nom bo kho is sold everywhere, but to enjoy the best Nom bo kho, tourists should visit the Hue nom restaurant on Ham Long Street and Long Vi On restaurant at No. 23 Ho Hoan Kiem Street. The price for a dish of nom bo kho is from VND20,000 ($1).
